    "title": "Cross-Experiment PRMP Meta-Analysis: Effect Sizes, Forest Plots & Moderator Analysis",
    "description": "Comprehensive meta-analysis pooling PRMP vs baseline results across 5 experiments (4 datasets, 8+ tasks). Includes Hedges' g effect sizes, DerSimonian-Laird random-effects pooling, subgroup analysis, meta-regression, and ablation validation.",
