    "conclusion_text": "Hypothesis PARTIALLY CONFIRMED: PRMP shows positive pooled effect (g=+0.430, p=0.4572), but pooled effect is not significant. PRMP tends to help, especially on regression tasks, but the specific regime prediction (high cardinality AND high predictability) is not validated.",
